{"2499670": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "性交製作人★ミ", "steam_appid": 2499670, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/a565db7896a7b3e6fd4ee377e1b72b51.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【性交製作人★ミ】一款由nikukyu製作，並由072 Project代理發行的短篇成人偶像養成遊戲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面臨即將倒閉的偶像事務所，身為製作人的你最終目標就是把最後的偶像&quot;夢咲&quot;培養成一名「完美的偶像」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/862bcd90fb139a262bfdb68f54382f7b.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你終於進了夢想中的製作公司0721Project。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是到職第一天就被告知0721要破產的資訊!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在快要破產的0721擔任最後的偶像「夢咲 文乃」的製作人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/9b097afe97b6fc709d7247787ed5b7c3.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「舞蹈」「歌唱」「技巧」「魅力」……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >參加4種不同的課程，以「N舞台」為目標努力!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/127512eaab6fe590d86dbff92124cafb.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和偶像性交並教育他的短篇模擬經營遊戲!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/482740024706c710f2ec9607437ba0f8.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為「文乃」的製作人，你要想盡辦法將她推上舞台，完成她的願望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為此，你必須妥善管理她的行程來提升她的各項能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >參加課程，或是面試各式各樣的小舞台等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以打工賺錢，掏自己的腰包幫文乃盛裝打扮，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文乃的夢想就由你來實現!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/2f62d96b04a645da94171c9649984fe8.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・跳過對話</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・隱藏對話框</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・全螢幕模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・事件回想</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・CG回想</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/a565db7896a7b3e6fd4ee377e1b72b51.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【性交製作人★ミ】一款由nikukyu製作，並由072 Project代理發行的短篇成人偶像養成遊戲。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面臨即將倒閉的偶像事務所，身為製作人的你最終目標就是把最後的偶像&quot;夢咲&quot;培養成一名「完美的偶像」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2499670/extras/862bcd90fb139a262bfdb68f54382f7b.avif?t=1762827675\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你終於進了夢想中的製作公司0721Project。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是到職第一天就被告知0721要破產的資訊!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在快要破產的0721擔任最後的偶像「夢咲 文乃」的製作人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite